sequenceDiagram
  participant Operator
  participant Nav
  participant Nav2
  participant Vision
  participant Camera
  participant BPU
  participant Merge
  participant LLM
  participant L610
  participant Huawei

  Operator->>Nav: start inspection
  Nav->>Nav2: navigate to station
  Nav2-->>Nav: arrive
  Nav->>Vision: trigger inspection
  Vision->>Camera: read latest frame
  Camera-->>Vision: frame
  Vision->>BPU: run inference
  BPU-->>Vision: detections
  Vision->>Merge: NMS and merge
  Merge-->>Vision: merged results
  Vision->>Vision: evaluate status
  alt mess detected
    Vision->>LLM: send ROI and prompt
    LLM-->>Vision: judgement
  end
  Vision->>L610: connect and publish
  L610-->>Huawei: MQTT report
  Huawei-->>L610: ack
  Vision-->>Nav: inspection result
  Nav->>Nav2: next station or home
